oral disturbances for patients with dementia and schizophrenia without fda approval in addition abbott marketed depakote for other psychiatric conditions in adults including depression anxiety obsessivecompulsive disorder posttraumatic stress disorder alcohol and drug withdrawal and psychiatric conditions in children including conduct disorders attention deficit disorder and autism the court also ordered abbott to a fiveyear term of probation and court supervision shareholders then brought derivative suits against the company directors for breach of fiduciary duty the parties reached a negotiated settlement in which abbott agreed to beef up its internal controls and paid the plaintiffs attorney fees sponsorshipedit since  abbott is the title sponsor of the world marathon majors see alsoedit list of biotechnology companies list of illinois companies list of pharmaceutical companies notes and referencesedit  a b c d e f  abbott annual report k   contacts  abbott us    abbott annual report k   abbott laboratories archived  july  at the wayback machine abbott laboratories retrieved july    abbott laboratories company history funding universe retrieved april     about us   its essential to be part of the extraordinary future india is building miles d white intodayin   grinspoon lester hedblom peter  the speed culture amphetamine use and abuse in america cambridge massachusetts harvard university press p  isbn  oclc    layne rachel lopatto elizabeth july   ge abbott end  billion diagnostic sale deal update bloomberg news   abbott press release february   abbott completes acquisition of solvay pharmaceuticals archived from the original on  march  retrieved march     abbott laboratories feb  current report form k filing date feb   pdf secdatabasecom retrieved dec     abbott press release march   abbott completes acquisition of starlims technologies archived from the original on  october  retrieved march     abbott  annual report p  abbott press release may   abbott to becom